<p>But along with SCROD, the RIAL, LILA Wallace, the grid left me hesitating as to whether I&#39;d give this one to a novice, attempting to get them hooked on crosswords. Didn&#39;t pass that test for me, so I felt like I couldn&#39;t give it the POW!</p>

